{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2479475,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Ali Ray","original_name":"Ali Ray","popularity":0.0923,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/sBtuuQ2MPliv76mjckkfwB3mNNO.jpg","id":1417181,"title":"Dawn of Impressionism: Paris 1874","original_title":"Dawn of Impressionism: Paris 1874","overview":"The Impressionists are the most popular group in art history – millions flock every year to marvel at their masterpieces. But, to begin with, they were scorned, penniless outsiders. 1874 was the year that changed everything; the first Impressionists, “hungry for independence”, broke the mould by holding their own exhibition outside official channels. Impressionism was born and the art world was changed forever.  What led to that first groundbreaking show 150 years ago? Who were the maverick personalities that wielded their brushes in such a radical and provocative way? The spectacular Musée d’Orsay exhibition brings fresh eyes to this extraordinary tale of passion and rebellion. The story is told not by historians and curators but in the words of those who witnessed the dawn of Impressionism: the artists, press and people of Paris, 1874.","poster_path":"/clqZ9pTHuii5KCzqRC2iXRnJsta.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.6394,"release_date":"2025-03-18","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":5.8,"vote_count":5},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/YHW4wQaUdtHjnvhZH4uQtsjfqt.jpg","id":607710,"title":"Frida Kahlo","original_title":"Frida Kahlo","overview":"She was a prolific self-portraitist, using the canvas as a mirror through all stages of her turbulent and, at times, tragic life. This highly engaging film takes us on a journey through the life of one of the most prevalent female icons: Frida Kahlo. Displaying a treasure trove of colour and a feast of vibrancy on screen, this personal and intimate film offers privileged access to her works and highlights the source of her feverish creativity, her resilience and her unmatched lust for life, men, women, politics and her cultural heritage.","poster_path":"/fzHHWd3dB2Dns936AWkEu7cJAUQ.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.2467,"release_date":"2020-06-15","softcore":false,"video":true,"vote_average":7.2,"vote_count":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/eyb9txvnuiyAYdtrpARmXxh3vSB.jpg","id":1185135,"title":"Klimt & The Kiss","original_title":"Klimt & The Kiss","overview":"The Kiss by Gustav Klimt is one of the most recognised and reproduced paintings in the world. It is perhaps the most popular poster on student dorm walls from Beijing to Boston.  Painted in Vienna around 1908, the evocative image of an unknown embracing couple has captivated viewers with its mystery, sensuality and dazzling materials ever since it was created. But just what lies behind the appeal of the painting – and just who was the artist that created it?  Delving into the details of real gold, decorative designs, symbolism and simmering erotica, a close study of the painting takes us to the remarkable turn of the century Vienna when a new world was battling with the old.","poster_path":"/orVeKxKtPegIyiQwEnTfrax90q9.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.3149,"release_date":"2023-10-30","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.0,"vote_count":2}]},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":5879856,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Ali Ray","original_name":"Ali Ray","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":"/zaEIxc0eyrEymgP3HOD9VcMvuBg.jpg","known_for":[]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":5722698,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ali Raymer","original_name":"Ali Raymer","popularity":0.0578,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/nEYl0uYPmP44BCosBsMkWjohIPM.jpg","id":311429,"title":"Tweeked","original_title":"Tweeked","overview":"Tweeked is the story of Carrie and Michelle, whose friendship disintegrates as they careen into a methamphetamine frenzy.","poster_path":"/n3LUeR8bNOc88MmcCYYrNGs1PUu.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2751,"release_date":"2001-03-08","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":10.0,"vote_count":1}]},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":5367088,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Rayhan Ali","original_name":"Rayhan Ali","popularity":0.0286,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/30jbD8Er4aB7FbfUbyZLORMDnJN.jpg","id":1241436,"title":"Warfare","original_title":"Warfare","overview":"A platoon of Navy SEALs embarks on a dangerous mission in Ramadi, Iraq, with the chaos and brotherhood of war retold through their memories of the event.","poster_path":"/l39TlELomwysfsr37vrvCV6rmaQ.jpg","media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[10752,28],"popularity":9.75,"release_date":"2025-04-09","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.086,"vote_count":1456}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":4895110,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Rayah Ali","original_name":"Rayah Ali","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"id":1336332,"title":"Inquiry Of Shadows","original_title":"Inquiry Of Shadows","overview":"\"Inquiry of Shadows\" is a documentary that delves into the hidden depths of the Uyghur genocide in China. Through personal accounts, expert insights, and historical analysis, the film unveils the dark nexus of psychological warfare, cultural obliteration, and the silencing of artistic and intellectual voices.","poster_path":null,"media_type":"movie","original_language":"en","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.0559,"release_date":"2024-09-09","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0}]},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3461907,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Ali Rayshouni","original_name":"Ali Rayshouni","popularity":0.0,"profile_path":null,"known_for":[{"adult":false,"b